{"tid":1198982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論 撤回逃犯條例只不過係緩兵之計","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T01:07:09.000Z","uid":222328,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed32df774892b8d6fc45777c466a167ee28385fd","tid":1198982,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"琴日一百萬人上街遊行，政府無動於衷。<br />\n如果我地星期二再和理非非，政府撤回逃犯條例都只不過係因為基於國際壓力，而唔係因為要對市民負責。<br />\n撤回逃犯條例只係政府緩兵之計。03年有第廿三條，19年有逃犯條例，過多幾年又再推過另一條惡法，咁到時又要再衝多次？ 個時已經冇人會再衝，衝得嘅都已經俾人拉哂。<br />\n再講，就算政府會撤回方案都係因為外國嘅壓力。你估過左今次，外資仲敢唔敢留係香港？應該會好似李嘉誠咁慢慢撤資。今次，佢地唔夠時間撤資。下次呢？錢都已經走哂，佢地仲會唔會理哩個地方？下次再推嘅時候，我地只有硬食。<br />\n今個星期二，可能最後一個機會有咁多香港人企出黎，我地要嘅唔單止係撤回逃犯條例，今次我地要一個服務香港人嘅政府，同香港人一齊對抗中央嘅政府。<br />\n衝得嘅話，今次一定唔可以輕易散去。"},{"pid":"9d4d187a6876f5de0296c614d78cfb8056446033","tid":1198982,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147b047fdcbd87c3cc1f1e0137cc59afa134fa07","tid":1198982,"uid":222328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0ffa1a0469a9da34b97f00acea3beda3369c5f","tid":1198982,"uid":194398,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:20:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b20542c6498b78128ad50da34039c15025bc097","tid":1198982,"uid":222328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a0ffa1a0469a9da34b97f00acea3beda3369c5f","tid":1198982,"uid":194398,"like":1,"dislike":7,"s